content:
Manage Beneficiaries as a Self-Service Process (Unmanaged Package)

Capture customer requests to add or modify beneficiaries through a self-service channel.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Configure a self-service portal using the Financial Services Client Portal template to give your customers a self-guided process to add or modify beneficiaries.
title: Self Service Beneficiary Management
